Update: Wednesday, April 3rd.  Sad to say things aren't running smoothly at Pizza D'Oro Columbia Heights location. We haven't ordered in awhile because of issues. Gave them another chance this evening but it was all for nothing.  When placing our delivery order, I asked the employee on the phone twice if blue cheese dressing & celery came with wings? He said yes. After I placed our order, I reminded him about the dressing & celery. He assured me those items would be included. I apologetically explained that the last few times we ordered, my husband did not receive celery or blue cheese dressing. He said don't worry. I thanked him & hung up.  Order arrives. Pizza is cold. Wings very hot AND no celery. Did receive blue cheese dressing but NO CELERY.  We will not try again. Bye bye.  Original 4 star review:  We've ordered pizza several times from Pizza D'Oro on 14th St NW in Columbia Heights and they've always been delicious.  Nice thin crust with savory pizza sauce and high quality mozzarella. We've had plain, mushroom & spinach and their white pizza - all were wonderful.  Nice friendly staff too.
